---
title: Savoury Bacon, Parmesan & Chive Pancakes with Cherry Tomatoes & Rocket | Serves 2
description: Craving pancakes but still want that savoury hit? We've got you covered with these cheesy bacon and chive pancakes drizzled
with herby mayo. Serve up with a side of cherry tomatoes for a burst of sweetness. We think there is no better way to start the
day!
